    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 represents the zenith of BMW M-division engineering. At its core is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system, delivering a visceral 7,900-RPM redline. This specimen features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis is pristine, with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein dampers. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a factory-fresh luster with zero oxidation, while the cabin is devoid of typical bolster wear or pixel failure. A mechanically peerless example with comprehensive service records.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
