    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows absolutely no signs of wear, inside or out. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a mirror-like finish, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium upholstery remains taut and unmarked, the dashboard is pristine, and the original factory scent lingers. Every switch, button, and electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with every service performed by certified specialists and fully documented. This is not merely a used car; it is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Perfect for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than the best.",
